sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Manager as Club Manager
    participant Gateway as API Gateway (:7000)
    participant ReportSvc as ReportService (:5103)
    participant ReportDB as SQL Server (Report DB)
    participant Redis as Redis Stream (clubreporthub-events)
    participant NotifSvc as NotificationService (:5105)
    participant NotifDB as SQL Server (Notification DB)

    Manager->>Gateway: POST /api/reports/{id}/submit (Bearer JWT)
    Gateway->>ReportSvc: Forward POST /api/reports/{id}/submit
    Note over ReportSvc: Validate report details count > 0 & Status is Draft/Rejected
    ReportSvc->>ReportDB: UPDATE Reports SET Status = 'UnderReview', SubmittedAtUtc = NOW
    ReportDB-->>ReportSvc: 1 Row Updated
    ReportSvc->>ReportDB: INSERT INTO AuditLogs (Action = 'Submit')
    ReportDB-->>ReportSvc: AuditLog Created

    ReportSvc->>Redis: XADD clubreporthub-events (RoutingKey: 'report.submitted', Payload: JSON)
    Redis-->>ReportSvc: RedisEntryId (e.g. 1784615916727-0)
    ReportSvc-->>Gateway: HTTP 200 OK (ReportResponse JSON)
    Gateway-->>Manager: HTTP 200 OK (Submitted Status)

    Note over NotifSvc: BackgroundService running XREADGROUP loop
    Redis->>NotifSvc: XREADGROUP deliver entry (1784615916727-0)
    NotifSvc->>NotifDB: SELECT COUNT(1) FROM ProcessedEvents WHERE EventId = @EventId
    NotifDB-->>NotifSvc: 0 (Not processed yet - Idempotent Check)
    NotifSvc->>NotifDB: INSERT INTO Notifications (...) & INSERT INTO ProcessedEvents (...)
    NotifDB-->>NotifSvc: Records Saved Successfully
    NotifSvc->>Redis: XACK clubreporthub-events notification-service 1784615916727-0
    Redis-->>NotifSvc: Message Acknowledged (Pending Count = 0)
